Patch for Flash Player that solves the "@" and all "AltGr" problems (wmode transparent/opaque).

It works for now on :
- Mozilla Firefox
- Google Chrome
- Safari (only MacOS)
- IE (tested ie 7,8,9)

How to use :

See Sample.as or :

new FlashAtFix(textfield_txt);

The "allowScriptAccess" parameter need to be set at "always" or "sameDomain".

To test it : http://goo.gl/HZucI
